    "image_with_text_b7bFYU": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_Ln3K8N": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "The Language of Frequency",
            "title_highlight_color": "#6d388b",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_KXRzbC": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>What you see here isn’t magic — it’s physics. When sound frequency passes through this metal plate, it reorganizes grains of sand into perfect geometric patterns.<br/><br/>Each tone creates a different shape — because every frequency carries a unique vibration that matter responds to.</p><p>Our <strong>Frequency Generator</strong> works on the same principle — but instead of sand, it’s your <strong>body, water, and energy field</strong> that align to those pure tones.<br/><br/>The result: balance, focus, and a state of resonance where manifestation becomes effortless.</p><p><em>(Real frequency. Real vibration. Real transformation.)</em></p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_Ln3K8N",
        "text_KXRzbC"
      ],
