    "image_with_text_ED9waL": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_3h9Hcz": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "The Science You Can See",
            "title_highlight_color": "#6d388b",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_9Atbm4": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>What you’re looking at isn’t theory — it’s proof.<br/><br/>Our <strong>Frequency Generator</strong> emits precise sinusoidal waves — the same kind of frequencies used in sound therapy, brainwave synchronization, and Schumann resonance calibration.</p><p>The screen displays the <em>exact vibration</em> your environment is being tuned to.<br/><br/>You’re not “imagining energy” — you’re witnessing it being measured, stabilized, and broadcast.</p><p>Every setting corresponds to a real, physical frequency that interacts with water molecules, nervous system signals, and even electromagnetic balance in your space.</p><p><strong>Visible frequency. Tangible harmony. Real transformation.</strong></p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
